    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――芸能事務所プレタポルテ・会議室",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Conference room in talent agency Pret-A-Porter.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 1.6666666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "もう察しはついていると思うけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m sure you’ve already figured it out‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.566666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "今の私はここのプロデューサーよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but I’m now a producer here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 7.966666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_02-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "新進気鋭の事務所のプロデューサー様か\nおめでとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The prestigious producer of an emerging talent agency‚ huh?\nCongratulations.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 13.233333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_02-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "世渡り上手ですなあ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Quite the corporate climber‚ huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.233333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 15.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あら、貴方達だって、移籍すれば同じことよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ transfer here‚ and you’ll have similar opportunities.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "契約書はすでに出来ているわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve already prepared the contracts.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.633333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "後は本人達にサインをしてもらうだけよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "All that’s needed is your signatures.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.566666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 24.466666666666665
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 25.466666666666665
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_02-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "……\n……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…\n…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.466666666666665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 26.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "待って下さい\nどうしていきなり彼女達の移籍話になるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please wait.\nWhy are we jumping straight into talk of a transfer?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "まずは全てを説明すべきです\nバンプロは、彼女達に多大な迷惑をかけたんですよ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You need to explain everything to us first.\nVan Productions caused them a great deal of trouble.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 37.96666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_02-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "同感だよ\n僕は子供かもしれないけど自分の意思は持っている",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ditto.\nI may still be a child‚ but I do have my own free will.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.666666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 43.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_02-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "急に移籍しろって言われて\nはい、分かりましたなんて言う訳ないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you ask me out of the blue to sign with you‚\nthere’s no way I’ll say‚ “Cool‚ let’s do it.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 49.36666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "葵はともかく{user}さんまで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aoi aside‚ I’m surprised‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "初めから話さないと分からないのかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Must I explain everything from the beginning for you to understand?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.833333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 54.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_02-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "うちは何か最初っから全部決まってた感じがして\n気持ち悪いなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m getting the feeling our fate was sealed from the very start.\nIt feels kinda gross.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 60.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ふふ、優は鋭いわね。{user}さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe. Aw‚ you’re a sharp girl‚ Yu.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 65.16666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "察しの悪い人間はこの業界で長生き出来ないわよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ dimwitted people don’t last long in this industry‚ you know?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.16666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "なんと思われても構いません\n説明をお願いします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t care what you think of me.\nPlease explain.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_serious-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 73.7
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 73.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "まず朝倉社長――いえ、私にとっては前社長ね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let’s start with my boss‚ Asakura… Well‚ former boss.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "彼は会社の資金を横領していました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "He was embezzling company funds.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.26666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "私はそのことを知って社員や所属アイドルを守るために",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I found out‚ I scrambled to do everything I could",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "奔走して、ここに拾ってもらったのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "to protect our staff and talent by getting hired here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "トリエルとリズノワを解雇するよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As for TRINITYAiLE and LizNoir’s dismissal‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.13333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "朝倉に仕向けたのも私よ。今後の貴方達のためにね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was the one who made Asakura do that—to give you girls a future.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 98.33333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（嘘だ。自分優位に話を進めようと脚色している）\n（そんな雰囲気がある）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（She’s lying. She’s twisting the story in a way that will make her look good.）\n（That’s the sense I’m getting.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 104.66666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_02-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "それ、おかしいよ。社長が不正をしてたら\n止めるのが普通じゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But that’s crazy. If your boss was breaking the law‚\nwouldn’t most people try to stop him first?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 110.66666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_02-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "そうやね。うちには姫野さんが社長の罪を利用して\nここに乗り換えたようにしか見えんわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Exactly. From where we’re standing‚ it looks a lot like you took advantage\nof Asakura-san’s crimes to get yourself here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 118.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_02-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "僕達を手土産にして？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Did you use us as dowry?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 120.83333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_06_02-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "そうや、そうちゃいますか。姫野さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s it‚ isn’t it‚ Himeno-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.83333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 125
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
